      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李益、霍小玉、送客甲、送客乙同上。送客乙（同白）请吓。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "送客甲"
      ],
      "text": "才子跨征鞍，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "思妇愁红玉。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲"
      ],
      "text": "芳草送莺啼，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "落花催马足。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "吓，君虞兄请了。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李益"
      ],
      "text": "二位请了。送客乙（同白）军中笳鼓喧鸣，良时吉日，早些起行罢。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "李益"
      ],
      "text": "实不相瞒，小玉姐话长，使人难别。送客乙（同白）古人云：“仗剑对樽酒，耻为离别颜。”男儿意气，为何留恋如此？",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "李益"
      ],
      "text": "咳！过来见了二位。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "霍小玉"
      ],
      "text": "二位。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "吓郡主，我们还要送君虞兄数程，回来自有平安寄上。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "霍小玉"
      ],
      "text": "多谢二位。送客乙（同白）军行有程，未可滞他行色。吓君虞兄，我们先往长亭恭候。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "李益"
      ],
      "text": "二位先请。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲",
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客甲"
      ],
      "text": "长旗掀落日。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "送客乙"
      ],
      "text": "短剑割离情。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "送客甲、送客乙同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "霍小玉"
      ],
      "text": "李郎，你去也罢，只是眼下呵！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902115_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902115",
      "scene_id": "70902115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
